      <title>‘5·18 산 증인’ 안성례 오월어머니집 초대 관장 별세</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/28/JOBYCAKEMZEZTFVIUDICVU5USI/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/28/JOBYCAKEMZEZTFVIUDICVU5USI/</guid>
